{"tid":1334224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7 2 1 要 人 呀 7 2 1 要 人 呀","createTime":"2019-07-20T04:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T04:58:56.000Z","uid":283781,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe287b407eacce42fda300286de95cffc7816ea9","tid":1334224,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:30:43.000Z","msg":"終於開到個連登ac 第一次開po<br />\n每次發夢我都企係前線<br />\n主要想講講tear 其實tear真係咁多款最廢<br />\n包實小小就真係唔驚 <br />\n次次都總會見到有人著短褲 唔包膠<br />\n我都明白真係好熱我都好怕熱<br />\n當個個都防到tear既時候 <br />\n就算佢射100粒我地都企定定<br />\n到時速龍衝我地都可以反打仲洗咩退<br />\n中tear真係唔好受 又勞煩到first aid<br />\n切勿濫用救護服務呀 大家生性小小好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後想講小小自己<br />\n屋企人雖然全黃 <br />\n不過次次都叫我唔好出 話好危險 博拉咩<br />\n7.1個次仲要打爆電話叫我返屋企<br />\n最後應承佢地唔入立會先冇事<br />\n當然最後有冇入就唔講了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出身係一個中產家庭既我出左事都可以走<br />\n但係其實冇人想走架<br />\n呢個地方由出世到生活 所有野都係度<br />\n有頭髮邊個想做癩痢架<br />\n就算機會渺茫 有得救都一定要出力救<br />\n<br />\n最後721真係要人呀 多你一個真係好多<br />\n香港加油 天祐我城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b03f2b391ee22e2d32f54454a1ca49e5f83018","tid":1334224,"uid":30163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:31:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 全部人同我出去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c83ede4696c6f6e8662c9b0ac4aed8eb38d75df6","tid":1334224,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0698164ce78e6eeb16f1a6528e8bcee90f5d7df6","tid":1334224,"uid":36157,"li